{"tid":1628431,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[幾句講完]有鑑於連登現時情況，請大家入來","createTime":"2019-10-06T02:50:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T03:06:08.000Z","uid":44592,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1239ec3e1198f93bf41cf8a00d6217679ba65a4d","tid":1628431,"uid":44592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:50:02.000Z","msg":"長話短說，我唔係係度「教你點做」同「解釋點解咁做」。<br />\n而係直接講「你要做咩」。<br />\n<br />\n首先所有野要維持下列原則，凡不符合以下原則的人請無視:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 - 缺一不可</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">不分化 不割蓆 BE WATER</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">兄弟爬山 各自修行</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">BE HUMBLE 意見不同請授教 認同與否均不應強烈反抗</span><br />\n<br />\n另外下列為大家當下要做的事：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">1. 所有前線行動，無需在連登睇風向，請各向前線TG圈自己傾自己搞自己做。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">2. 連登並非大台，凡涉及吹風的PO（如分化、割蓆、和理超人上身），一律當三毛五毛假膠處理。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">3. 文宣繼續做要做的事同而家做緊的事，主要解釋裝修、改善日程表。（太密了，長期抗爭不應該日日有地方去，反正已有國際關注）</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">4. 反滲透。（例如大家明知將故事剪頭剪尾的三色台）</span>"},{"pid":"dc483b63bae2ca9f9530a040bc817b31b4471b2b","tid":1628431,"uid":299104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:53:31.000Z","msg":"講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2eJKVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2eJKVS.png&h=fd892c2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GobPu5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGobPu5a.jpg&h=8c19a255&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yYDlCk4w_-I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyYDlCk4w_-I&d=15TDSCYqMG0%2FxcOE0oxfEMpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=91645881\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yYDlCk4w_-I</a>"},{"pid":"44ce279b203511974b4d19fd73482d07a550f47a","tid":1628431,"uid":191052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:02:27.000Z","msg":"不割席不篤灰不分化不指罵<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n支持前線的所有決定<br />\n不回分化撚風向撚冷氣軍師post"},{"pid":"cbd75fe2bbdcfe98c09547d4361f221952845c4f","tid":1628431,"uid":44592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:06:08.000Z","msg":"剛剛開錯台, 轉新PO + 補充<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1628472/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1628472/page/1</a><br />\n請讓此PO沉"}]}